{"tid":1411780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人到咗呢個moment已經唔想再執著於撤唔撤回？","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:53:40.000Z","uid":268540,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5b079fdc5fa13df66e0f7e4853ce88506f4410","tid":1411780,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"佢一日唔撤回，香港人先會有理由咁不斷抗爭同借機會爭取埋2014年我地已經想要嘅嘢。我呢個moment最想係永久雙普選同制裁警狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c816c1759f4f455e1a6e63bdb2d6fe47b21cc1b","tid":1411780,"uid":22104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：特首林鄭</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：次次聽到林鄭開記者會都好嬲</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾並唔係我地香港人嘅特首<br />\n<br />\n當別人說：你個特首好垃圾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不要說：夠係你個特首</span><br />\n試著說：嗰件垃圾並唔係我地香港人選出黎嘅，所以佢並唔係我地特首<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不要只在心裡想佢辭職<br />\n我地要喺言語上行為上罷免佢<br />\n我地香港人已經罷免咗佢<br />\n<br />\n<ins>不分藍色黃色撐反送中撐警</ins><br />\n所有香港人都覺得佢係垃圾，佢就係一件垃圾<br />\n我地香港人罷免佢</strong>"},{"pid":"8373fe3f0c069c984c752599a4f8b218d38c4175","tid":1411780,"uid":272580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5b079fdc5fa13df66e0f7e4853ce88506f4410","tid":1411780,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"佢一日唔撤回，香港人先會有理由咁不斷抗爭同借機會爭取埋2014年我地已經想要嘅嘢。我呢個moment最想係永久雙普選同制裁警狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"當然係雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4000766076c8c9dea055cd6252857fb7aa3dbe39","tid":1411780,"uid":149611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 , 缺一不可"},{"pid":"00b7c